/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27560,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/15\/ibn-abbas-tasting-food-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":24850,"position":2},"title":"Ibn Abbas on Fasting: Permission to taste food while fasting if needed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Qudamah reported: Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThere is nothing wrong for a fasting person to taste food, vinegar, or something he wants to purchase.\u201d Ahmad ibn Hanbal said, \u201cI prefer to avoid tasting food, but there is no harm and nothing wrong if it\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24885,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/05\/29\/fasting-ghibah-ruined-sawm\/","url_meta":{"origin":24850,"position":3},"title":"Abu Aliyah on Fasting: Backbiting ruins fasting as worship","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 29, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn al-Sari reported: Abu al-\u2018Alyiah, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cThe fasting person is in an act of worship as long as he does not backbite anyone, even if he is sleeping on his bed.\u201d Source: al-Zuhd li Hanna\u0304d ibn al-Sari\u0304 1202 \u0639\u0646 \u0647\u0646\u0627\u062f \u0628\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0631\u064a \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34167,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/04\/30\/acts-of-worship-spoiled\/","url_meta":{"origin":24850,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Worship: Acts of worship spoiled by insincerity and sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 30, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cOne who fasts might only acquire hunger and thirst from his fasting. One who stands for prayer might only acquire fatigue from his prayer.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 13413 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27943,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/20\/angels-bless-breaking-fast-together\/","url_meta":{"origin":24850,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: Angels bless those who break their fast together","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 20, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn al-Zubayr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, broke his fast with Sa\u2019d ibn Mu\u2019adh and he said, \u201cThe fasting have broken their fast with you, the righteous have eaten your food, and the angels send blessings upon you.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 1747\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","sr